## 七、CSS Override 参考（补充到 el-overrides.css）

```css
/* ===== Dropdown Menu Panel ===== */
.el-dropdown-menu,
.el-select-dropdown {
  border-radius: var(--radius-md) !important;   /* 6px */
  box-shadow: 0 4px 14px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06) !important;
  padding: 6px 0;
}

/* ===== Dropdown Item / Select Option ===== */
.el-dropdown-menu__item,
.el-select-dropdown__item {
  height: 40px;
  padding: 10px 20px;
  font-size: 14px;
  font-weight: 400;
  line-height: 20px;
  color: #6e6b7b;
}

.el-dropdown-menu__item:not(.is-disabled):hover,
.el-select-dropdown__item:hover:not(.is-disabled) {
  background: rgba(var(--pcv-brand-rgb), 0.05);
  color: #66666c;
}

.el-dropdown-menu__item.is-active,
.el-select-dropdown__item.selected {
  color: var(--pcv-brand);
  font-weight: 500;
  background: transparent;
}

.el-dropdown-menu__item.is-disabled,
.el-select-dropdown__item.is-disabled {
  color: #b2b2b8;
}
```

